_Woods\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the meme featuring Dae-han and Dike\\u00e7 is not the only Paris Olympics image being used humorously by Catholics.\", \"from\": 4812, \"to\": 4925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4915, \"end\": 4924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3584302676593295e-24, \"text\": \"Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A photo of the American, Irish and Italian flags displayed together at an Olympic medal ceremony has also been captioned by users to highlight the unique cultural heritage of Catholicism in the Eastern United States.\", \"from\": 4927, \"to\": 5143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4942, \"end\": 4950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999985560363223, \"rank\": 1.4435791718864574e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4952, \"end\": 4957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 0.8331619721743949, \"rank\": 0.19973895932167524, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 4962, \"end\": 4969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9999999994652171, \"rank\": 5.318644025900249e-10, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Average Catholic school on the East Coast,\\\"wrote one userabove the image of the three flags.\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5154, \"end\": 5169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cath